.SH NAME
stats \- Show aggregate site statistics.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
stats
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Shows the latest aggregate site statistics available to the session, including the current connection or freshness status.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
$ stats
.fi
